This project is a community recreation of the "/buddy" companion feature
that was originally part of Claude Code (https://claude.ai/claude-code),
a product of Anthropic, PBC.

The original companion system, its concept, design, and implementation
are the intellectual property of Anthropic, PBC. This project reverse-
engineers and reimplements the feature using Claude Code's public
extensibility mechanisms (custom commands, CLAUDE.md, hooks).

The companion data (species, rarities, stats, ASCII art, generation
prompts) were extracted from publicly distributed Claude Code binaries
(v2.1.92) and are attributed to Anthropic, PBC.

Claude Code: https://github.com/anthropics/claude-code
Anthropic: https://www.anthropic.com
